<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-60-0265 </DOCNO><TEXT>The paper deals with the main guide-lines for acceleration of scientificand technical progress in opencast and underground coal mining, coalpreparation, coal mining engineering and science. The paper presentssome results of planned means implementation aimed at an annual coaloutput of 780-800 Mt by 1990, the increase to be achieved due to a higherlabour productivity, while improving coal quality and developing saferand more comfortable working conditions for the miners. 3 figs.</TEXT></DOC>